Organization information.

Source: R/data.R
org_info.Rd

org.duns is a unique identifier that links the org_info and project_orgs tables.

Usage

org_info

Format

A data frame with 4 variables: org.duns, org.city, org.state and org.name

Source

http://exporter.nih.gov/ExPORTER_Catalog.aspx?sid=3&index=0

Note

Be wary of this table as the DUNS reporting in the NIH EXPORTER was not previously correct for years 2000-2008.
